nodes.text: This person was the first officer of a pirate crew at some point after 32 BBY. This person was the second in command to the pirate captain.

At some point, the brawler crewbeing Tantor discussed with the captain and jettisoned the captain to outer space. The first officer replaced the captain and, mistrusting Tantor, decided to shackle the brawler for the other crewmember's safety. In the following stepover, Tantor fred himself and escaped, killing a number of pirates in his way.
